    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is the game about:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a cataclysmic event rendered Earth uninhabitable, humanity was forced to flee their home planet in search of a new beginning. After centuries of interstellar travel, they discovered several planets suitable for colonization. However, these new worlds were barren and resource-poor, forcing humanity to resort to scavenging for survival. As a Star Scavenger, you are at the forefront of this struggle, venturing into the unknown to secure the resources necessary for humanity's survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290340/extras/e293dee5bb775c6ef542da95b425aa84.avif?t=1745288499\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290340/extras_big/e293dee5bb775c6ef542da95b425aa84.avif?t=1745288499 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration:</strong> Discover new planets and uncover hidden resources.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collection:</strong> Gather a variety of scrap to complete your objectives.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat:</strong> Fight off dangerous alien creatures to protect yourself and your team.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival:</strong> Adapt to harsh environments and overcome numerous challenges.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time is of the Essence:</strong> Each planet has its own unique time dilation, forcing you to work swiftly and efficiently.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Teamwork:</strong> Coordinate with your crew to overcome the challenges of each mission.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Planets:</strong> Explore a variety of alien worlds, each with its own unique environments and dangers.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abundant Loot:</strong> Collect a wide range of scrap, from common metals to rare energy crystals.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Combat:</strong> Engage in thrilling battles against ferocious alien creatures.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290340/extras/f5752d0b24d2524190cb3ee9a63817c1.poster.avif?t=1745288499\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290340/extras/f5752d0b24d2524190cb3ee9a63817c1.webm?t=1745288499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290340/extras/f5752d0b24d2524190cb3ee9a63817c1.mp4?t=1745288499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join us and become a Star Scavenger. The fate of humanity rests in your hands!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join Discord:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290340/extras/a7b6a76d86f9046cbb27d36200fb4f1c.avif?t=1745288499\" width=720 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
